### 1. 具体的优化代码或配置

#### 1.1 统一异常处理机制 (Java/Spring Boot 示例)
*目标：解决异常处理不统一，提升接口规范化。*

```java
@RestControllerAdvice
@Slf4j
public class SymphonyGlobalExceptionHandler {

    @ExceptionHandler(Exception.class)
    public ResponseEntity<Result<?>> handleException(Exception ex) {
        // 统一日志记录，包含TraceID
        MDC.put("errorCode", "SYS_ERROR");
        log.error("System error occurred", ex);

        return ResponseEntity.status(500).body(Result.fail(500, "系统繁忙，请稍后重试"));
    }

    @ExceptionHandler(BusinessException.class)
    public ResponseEntity<Result<?>> handleBusinessException(BusinessException ex) {
        log.warn("Business error: {}", ex.getMessage());
        return ResponseEntity.status(ex.getErrorCode()).body(Result.fail(ex.getErrorCode(), ex.getMessage()));
    }
}
```

#### 1.2 模块解耦与领域事件配置 (Spring Event/Message Queue)
*目标：降低模块耦合度，改用异步事件驱动。*

```java
// 领域事件定义
public class OrderCreatedEvent {
    private String orderId;
    private BigDecimal amount;
    // getters, setters
}

// 发布服务
@Service
public class OrderService {
    @Autowired private ApplicationEventPublisher eventPublisher;

    public void createOrder(Order order) {
        // ... 核心订单逻辑 ...
        // 发布事件，解耦库存、积分模块
        eventPublisher.publishEvent(new OrderCreatedEvent(order.getId(), order.getAmount()));
    }
}

// 监听器（在其他模块中）
@Component
public class InventoryListener {
    @EventListener
    public void handleOrderCreated(OrderCreatedEvent event) {
        // 异步处理库存扣减
        inventoryService.deduct(event.getOrderId());
    }
}
```

#### 1.3 可观测性配置
*目标：解决可观测性不足，集成链路追踪。*

```yaml
# application.yml
management:
  tracing:
    sampling:
      probability: 1.0 # 100% 采样，生产环境可调整
  zipkin:
    tracing:
      endpoint: http://zipkin-server:9411/api/v2/spans
  metrics:
    tags:
      application: symphony-core
    export:
      prometheus:
        enabled: true

logging:
  pattern:
    level: "%5p [${spring.application.name},%X{traceId},%X{spanId}]"
```

#### 1.4 自动化回归测试与质量门禁 (Jenkinsfile/groovy)
*目标：解决回归成本高，平衡鲁棒性与速度。*

```groovy
pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn clean package -DskipTests'
            }
        }
        stage('Unit Test') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn test'
                // 发布单元测试覆盖率
                jacoco execPattern: 'target/jacoco.exec'
            }
        }
        stage('Quality Gate') {
            steps {
                // 代码静态检查
                sh 'mvn sonar:sonar -Dsonar.qualitygate.wait=true'
            }
        }
        stage('Regression Test - Critical Path') {
            // 仅运行核心链路回归，平衡速度
            steps {
                sh 'mvn verify -Dgroups=CriticalPath'
            }
        }
    }
}
```

